select id,
       employeecode,
       organcode,
       routecode,
       employeetype,
       qualification,
       postcode,
       name,
       sex,
       birthday,
       identitycard,
       contactaddress,
       dwellingplace,
       telephone,
       mobile,
       email,
       photo,
       cardissued,
       recordstatus,
       creator,
       createtime,
       writeoffman,
       writeofftime,
       modifyrecord,
       password
  from employee;
column9: 从源数据库取得数据的sql语句，如果需要使用嵌套、关联查询，需在这配置完整sql，优先使用该配置项;未配置即会由列属性拼接
插入数据时优先使用insert配置，未配置insert时，程序根据列属性拼接insert
插入数据前先执行的sql语句
插入数据后再执行的sql语句
